  "text": "Starting systematic update of all monorepo packages to use the two-step ESM build process. Need to examine current state of each package (compiler, linter, plugin-cursor, testing, parser, core) and convert them to match the working types package pattern:\n\n1. Convert to pure ESM with \"type\": \"module\"\n2. Update build scripts to use bun + tsc two-step process\n3. Update dev scripts with watch mode\n4. Update exports to pure ESM format\n5. Clean up tsconfig.build.json files\n6. Remove tsup dependencies\n\nThis is a systematic refactor to standardize the build process across the entire monorepo.",
